MOF Name: C9H12CaO10<|>calcium trimesate synthesized by one-pot self-assembly reaction
Justification: The MOF C9H12CaO10 matches the CSD Ref Code OWEZEW01 based on several key features. The metal node is calcium (Ca), which matches the metal node in the CSD reference. The space group is P21/c, which is the same as the one provided in the CSD reference. The lattice parameters a, b, and c are 10.1977 Å, 16.4581 Å, and 7.4796 Å, respectively, which match the parameters given in the CSD reference. Additionally, the molecular formula C9H12CaO10 is consistent with the description of the calcium trimesate synthesized by the one-pot self-assembly reaction in the document. These matching features confirm that this MOF corresponds to the CSD Ref Code OWEZEW01.
